{"tid":1578613,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［廣傳］請所有831傷者現身說法，及定下不自殺聲明！","createTime":"2019-09-18T08:00:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T13:32:48.000Z","uid":167634,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"28b2db0e93b5f1962168d74b41db17d82622e1fc","tid":1578613,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:00:15.000Z","msg":"手動傳到比佢地睇到為止<br />\n<br />\n因為班狗同消防高層已經掩唔住件事<br />\n佢地唯一可以做就係不斷作故仔<br />\n由madam話唔知點解會少左三個<br />\n到依家又公開到原來最少有兩個紅色傷者轉為黃色，甘已經同佢地之前係記招嘅說法有出入<br />\n而令大眾對消防失去信任<br />\n<br />\n依家消防將有關傷者級別公開，所謂「澄清」又係咪事實呢？依家將個波拋左去傷者身上嘅你地，就只有你地可以澄清事實嘅真相！<br />\n<br />\n但前提，係依家充滿白色恐怖嘅香港入面，發出不自殺聲明係最起碼保障自身安全嘅第一步。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24afc670094ed1f85564c2a8ca221c2941d21b98","tid":1578613,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:01:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"20bce054d3d503b436f644994d56067be4b51790","tid":1578613,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:01:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4878b5f6e66a642b87b61e1f34fd5bfdf27badf8","tid":1578613,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:01:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"81636c564132928a60410d1712aa7a4e4dad6de4","tid":1578613,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:01:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"07c6a0bc7e2a836c260e65dc2bc6a31b4e17f8a2","tid":1578613,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:01:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"247bced835b727ee0cacbe511f3e7ae4e96e2eb4","tid":1578613,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:02:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f61990f7d5a85b45e5005a2a38e4c7301d7dd018","tid":1578613,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:02:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aa2a0373c35518775cb04ad6004cb5abf7b00dc9","tid":1578613,"uid":167634,"li